      <title>Java基础知识(二)</title>
      <link href="/2019/07/29/Java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86-%E4%BA%8C/"/>
      <url>/2019/07/29/Java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86-%E4%BA%8C/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Java基础学习笔记（二）</p><a id="more"></a><hr><h2 id="switch语句"><a href="#switch语句" class="headerlink" title="switch语句"></a>switch语句</h2><ul><li>switch语句的的表达式，只能是如下的6种数据类型之一：<br><em>Byte、short、char、int、枚举类型（jdk5.0新增）、String（jdk7.0新增）</em></li></ul><hr><h2 id="break-amp-continue"><a href="#break-amp-continue" class="headerlink" title="break &amp; continue"></a>break &amp; continue</h2><ul><li><p>break语句能用在switch和循环结构中，continue只能用在循环结构中。</p></li><li><p>continue和break默认跳出距离最近的一条循环或者语句，可以加标签使得结束外层循环。</p></li></ul><hr><h2 id="数组"><a href="#数组" class="headerlink" title="数组"></a>数组</h2><ul><li><p>数组是引用数据类型。</p></li><li><p>数组会默认初始化值。</p></li><li><p>数组声明时的数字可以是变量。</p></li></ul><hr><h3 id="数组打印问题"><a href="#数组打印问题" class="headerlink" title="数组打印问题"></a>数组打印问题</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[]&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(arr);<span class="comment">//地址值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span>[] arr1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">char</span>[]&#123;a, b, c&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(arr1);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：abc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>原因：在 Java 的println()方法重载中有一个方法为println(char[] a) 方法体为遍历该char型数组。</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
